# VibeScaffold — Quick Home Screen Demo
# Run: vhs demos/quick.tape

Output demos/quick.gif

Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Padding 20

Type "vs"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Navigate with arrows
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Up
Sleep 500ms
Up
Sleep 500ms

# Go to doctor
Type "2"
Sleep 2s

# Back
Type "q"
Sleep 1s

# Quit
Type "q"
Sleep 1s
